OL,3,CMore than 30,000 properties without
OL,4,Cwater due to burst main
OL,6,FMore than 30,000 properties in part of
OL,7,FEast Sussex are without water due to a
OL,8,Fburst water main.
OL,10,FCustomers in St Leonards-on-Sea,
OL,11,FHastings and areas in and around
OL,12,FWestfield are among those affected.
OL,14,FThe incident began at around 4.30pm on
OL,15,FThursday (2 May) after a water main
OL,16,Fburst in an area of dense woodland. It
OL,17,Fmeans the water supply works at
OL,18,FBeauport is not receiving the normal
OL,19,Fflow.
