OL,6,FSouthern Water says its teams worked
OL,7,Fthrough the night to get machinery and
OL,8,Fequipment ready to start making the
OL,9,Frepair on Friday (3 May).
OL,11,FIt's thought that the incident will
OL,12,Fcontinue into the weekend. This is
OL,13,Fbecause even if the repair is finished
OL,14,Ftoday, the company says it will take
OL,15,Fat least 24 hours to recharge and
OL,16,Fstart the supply works up again.
OL,18,FThree bottled water stations have been
OL,19,Fset up in the following locations:
