OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,FSouthern Water said: "We are
OL,8,Fcontinuing to deliver bottled water to
OL,9,Four vulnerable customers on our
OL,10,FPriority Services Register.
OL,12,F"Our helpline number for vulnerable
OL,13,Fcustomers needing access to bottled
OL,14,Fwater as a priority, or for other
OL,15,Fcustomer queries relating to the
OL,16,Fsupply interruption, is 0330 303 0368.
OL,18,F"We are very sorry for the impact and
OL,19,Finconvenience this is causing, and are
OL,20,Fdoing everything we can to restore
OL,21,Fsupplies."
